definition.value: An amino disaccharide consisting of an alpha-D-glucopyranose residue and a 2-acetamido-2-deoxy-alpha-D-allopyranose residue joined in sequence by a (1->4) glycosidic bond.
An amino disaccharide consisting of a beta-L-threo-hex-4-enopyranuronse residue and a 2-acetamido-2-deoxy-beta-D-glucopyranose residue joined in sequence by a (1->4) glycosidic bond.
